'''天主教馬老奇總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Meraukensis}}；{{lang-id|Keuskupan Agung Merauke}}）是[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[總教區|總教區]]，也是該國十個總教區之一。總教區位於[[巴布亞省|巴布亞省]]東南部，下轄[[天主教阿加茨暨阿斯馬特教區|阿加茨暨阿斯馬特]]、[[天主教马诺夸里暨索龙教区|馬諾誇里暨索龍]]、[[天主教蒂米卡教區|蒂米卡]]和[[天主教查亞普拉教區|查亞普拉]]四個教區，2003年時有122,500名教友、26個堂區和36名司鐸。<ref name="archbishop">{{cite news|publisher = UCA News |date = 2004-05-12|title = New Archbishop In Papua Seeks To Build Cooperation Among All Church Sectors|url = http://www.ucanews.com/2004/05/12/new-archbishop-in-papua-seeks-to-build-cooperation-among-all-church-sectors/}}{{Dead link|date=2018年10月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

總主教現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]，榮休總主教為{{link-id|尼各老·阿迪·塞普圖拉|Nicolaus Adi Seputra}}。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 28.03.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/03/28/200328b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-03-29 |language=en |date=2020-03-28 |archive-date=2020-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414053214/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/03/28/200328b.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

宗座代牧區於1950年6月24日因[[天主教安汶教區|安汶宗座代牧區]]分拆而設立<ref>{{cite book |title=APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=XVIII |year=1951 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=61-63 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-43-1951-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-03-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329082908/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-43-1951-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-03-29 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1966年11月15日升為總教區<ref>{{cite web |title=MERAUKENSIS |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19661115_meraukensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-03-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329082018/https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19661115_meraukensis.html |archivedate=2020-03-29 |language=la |date=1966-11-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

